 <text id="F6065T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Jacob Middows sends his pay to his friend George Brewer to pass along to his mother through
     Joseph Rock. He also includes a sum from George Gates to his father.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-08-18">August 18 1864</date>
      <name type="place">Camp Near Petersburg</name>
     </dateline>
     <salute>Dear Friend George W. Brewer</salute>
    </opener>

    <p><orig reg="I'll">ile</orig> state to you that I <orig reg="expressed">Exspressed</orig>
     $110.00 Dollars to you And you <orig reg="please">Pleas</orig> And Let Joseph Rock of <orig
      reg="Quincy">Quincey</orig> Township Franklin <orig reg="County">Countey</orig> Pennsylvania
     Lift it And give it to My Mother E Middows And George Gates sent 50 00 <abbr expan="dollars"
     >Do</abbr> to <unclear>
      <orig reg="you">hyou</orig>
     </unclear> and his father of George Gates of Quincy Township Franklin <orig reg="County"
      >Countey</orig> Pennsylvania is to lift his so if <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="comes">coms</orig> for it <orig reg="you'll">youl</orig> give it to them that is if
     I <orig reg="should">shold</orig> of gots <orig reg="should">shold</orig>
     <orig reg="happens">happns</orig> to Lose our <orig reg="receipts">Resiets</orig> that <orig
      reg="they">tha</orig><pb n="2"/> Can Draw it but if I <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> lose the
      <orig reg="receipt">Resiet</orig>
     <orig reg="I'll">ile</orig> send it to <orig reg="them">then</orig> then <orig reg="they"
     >tha</orig> can draw it</p>

    <closer>
     <salute>Yours<lb/>
      <orig reg="Truly">Truley</orig></salute>
     <signed>Jacob Middows<lb/> &amp;<lb/> George Gates.</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">And by So doing <orig reg="you'll">youl</orig> Oblige your Friends G
      Gates and Jacob Middows <name type="recipient">to George W Brewer<lb/> Chambersburg<lb/>
       Franklin<lb/> County <lb/><orig reg="Pennsylvania">Pensylvania</orig></name>
     </seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
